responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "C91E2B6149E384BF38929A997056EACC", "Some of our scouts have spotted groups of Forsaken Blade in Gravepeak, perhaps to pay respects at the family crypt of House Xander, but more likely they\'re robbing graves. They say the families of noble houses are buried among relics of power. If they\'re guarding something up there, it\'s no doubt they\'ve found something to use against the Kaelar. If you\'re thinking of traveling there, report anything we can use to counter them.")
